#
# and verify it parses with: `gh api repos/:owner/:repo/codeowners/errors`.

# .github/CODEOWNERS
#
# Routes review requests by changed path. GitHub counts CODEOWNERS approval
# per team — multi-team lines REQUIRE one approval per listed team.
# Combined with `.github/rulesets/protected-paths.json` `required_reviewers: 2`,
# sensitive lines below enforce the two-person two-team rule (AGENTS.md §10).
#
# This file is in policies/protected-paths.yml deny: — touches-policy label
# auto-applies; needs two-team approval (governance + security) to change.

